## Color

Defined in `styles/_variables.scss`. Document the intent here; the SCSS holds the values.

| Token | Role | _(todo: value)_ |
|---|---|---|
| `$color-bg` | page background | |
| `$color-surface` | raised surface | |
| `$color-primary` | single accent — used sparingly | |
| `$color-text` / `$color-text-muted` | text ramp | |

Rule: **one accent.** Semantic colors (warn / success / danger) only when something is genuinely that state.

## Typography

Font stacks live in `styles/_fonts.scss` (one `@import url(...)` for all web fonts).

| Variable | Used for | _(todo: stack)_ |
|---|---|---|
| `$font-heading` | display / headings | |
| `$font-body` | body copy | |
| `$font-label` | labels / mono data | |

Rule: components reference `$font-*` variables — **never** a raw `font-family` string.

## Spacing & radii

Use the `$space-*` and `$radius-*` scales in `_variables.scss`. Do not introduce ad-hoc pixel values; extend the scale instead.

## Component design

- Prefer small, single-purpose components; break sections into discrete, reusable pieces.
- Per-component SCSS; `.mobile.scss` companion only when the mobile variant materially differs.
- Reuse before creating — consult [`COMPONENT_INDEX.md`](./COMPONENT_INDEX.md) first.

